    	change input start and stop to uint
    	added type conversions to avoid warnings under codesys 3.0

    hm	23. mar. 2009	rev 1.4
    	avoid writing to input stop

    hm	12. nov. 2009 rev 1.5
    	limit start and stop to size -1

